PROJECT BOX REQUIREMENTS


It is requested to create a class called Box with the following characteristics:

   • Must have 3 integer attributes (width, height, and depth)
   • It must have 2 constructors, one empty and one with 3 arguments, one
     for each attribute of the class.
   • You must have the method that calculates the volume of the box according to the
     formula of the previous sheet. FORMULA VOLUME:  Volume = width * height * depth
   • Create a test class to create an object of type box that has
     as values: width = 3, height = 2, depth = 6 and send to print
     the volume of the box according to the values provided
     previously